{"tid":432910,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"下任特首有咩熱門？","createTime":"2017-10-12T02:50:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-23T17:26:32.000Z","uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"cb498c38931034f62c6fad644eec1d212487f818","tid":432910,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T02:50:53.000Z","msg":"出於一個純八卦嘅好奇心態，我就做過一啲資料搜集。<br />\n<br />\n陳智思好明顯夠班，但係佢講過未來五至十年都唔會選特首 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實啱嘅，佢有家族生意，點會想坐個吃力不討好嘅位<br />\n<br />\n當今政務司太老喇，應該無機<br />\n<br />\n財爺波叔家陣都幾乎俾林鄭架空啦，似乎都唔掂 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n按慣例律政司就唔會更上一層樓嘅，何況佢出返私人市場做資深大狀咪搵得重多 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢都唔似有政治野心<br />\n<br />\n葉劉/薯片太老，應該無法子捲土重來 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n劉鳴偉/李慧瓊太嫩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁睇係咪得返邱騰華一個潛在人選？"},{"pid":"f6d2211d83c17c79ce20514b71d7ce1f3b6543f8","tid":432910,"uid":51978,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T02:52:56.000Z","msg":"唔記得講重點，就係林鄭表明，自己無意爭取連任，完成任期後會將自己「還給林生(丈夫林兆波)」！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.orangenews.hk/news/system/2017/05/21/010058556.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.orangenews.hk%2Fnews%2Fsystem%2F2017%2F05%2F21%2F010058556.shtml&d=6mBMeeO8Haym%2FeubmfjcPxv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=ad6e57a7\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.orangenews.hk/news/system/2017/05/21/010058556.shtml</a>"},{"pid":"6271d8dc2fea4796936c620f6cdf697352af161d","tid":432910,"uid":53773,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T02:53:19.000Z","msg":"仲有袁國強<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0effde21d111de91cc6ffaa85c2ad7a59feab41","tid":432910,"uid":62850,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T02:58:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote