d":"56ed500a5c1b28c4f6c52eac16155d8d5f495f9a","tid":432910,"uid":51978,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T03:06:04.000Z","msg":"聶德權似有啲潛質 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://ce2017.appledaily.com.hk/articles/1_56848967\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fce2017.appledaily.com.hk%2Farticles%2F1_56848967&d=6mBMeeO8Haym%2FeubmfjcPxv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=68d8e652\" target=\"_blank\">http://ce2017.appledaily.com.hk/articles/1_56848967</a><br />\n<br />\n新任政制及內地事務局局長聶德權現時53歲，開始為政界熟悉源於他09年擔任社會福利署署長，當時他有「三耳署長」稱號，<span style=\"color: red;\">勤快及熟書作風深獲黨派讚賞，連時任政務司司長的林鄭月娥亦另眼相看</span>，2013年6月至12月特別調任為政務司司長私人辦公室專員（特別職務），與林鄭拍住上專責處理人口政策，其後任新聞處處長，<span style=\"color: red;\">與傳媒建立良好關係，其後任食衞局常秘，亦與黨派有商有量，政圈風評不俗。</span><br />\n<br />\n政制及內務事務局局長譚志源大讚「接班人」聶德權，指對方曾任學生會會長，當時已經「好威」，86年加入政府<span style=\"color: red;\">曾任駐京辦主任，了解內地事務</span>，出任新聞處長期間亦曾與他一同陪梁振英訪問內地，並參與過政改，故此是有經驗之人，直言由聶出任下屆局長是「<span style=\"color: red;\">深慶得人</span>」。"},{"pid":"54ad374a75b748aa1fa50eb0d83968bd53b2b352","tid":432910,"uid":20867,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T04:33:25.000Z","msg":"鞭啦<br />\n<br />\n中共一早已欽點薯片（2）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/262100/page/27?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/262100/page/27?ref=ios</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"595addefe408835614be6fb53df1836158690bcb","tid":432910,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T04:35:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>鞭啦<br />\n<br />\n中共一早已欽點薯片（2）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/262100/page/27?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/262100/page/27?ref=ios</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\